{
  "texts": [
    "We then analysed the data within each framework section and developed our findings.",
    "Relevant data that did not fit into the framework were analysed thematically.",
    "We used a thematic analysis approach as described by Miles and Huberman [72] as referred to in Carroll 2013 [66] in their paper on best fit framework synthesis.",
    "New themes were generated based on our interpretation of the evidence and constant comparison of the new themes across the included studies.",
    "In accordance with best fit framework synthesis methods, we inductively expanded the a priori framework to include a section on person-centred care and communication to reflect the breadth of all our findings."
  ]
}